          <p><h5>Word Herd begins its work by scraping the web for articles related to your query.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
            Next, it takes the first 100 significant words of those articles, removing <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stop_words">stopwords</a> like "the", "a" and "that".</h5></p>


